1
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:26,400
I, Hu Linglong, am indeed a woman.

2
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,280
You can't tell them.

3
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:31,039
It's over.

4
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,440
Linglong.

5
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:33,240
This...

6
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:34,960
Even so,

7
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:35,960
so what?

8
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:40,400
You...

9
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,259
You see this...

10
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,400
Years of hard work,

11
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,360
all in vain.

12
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:48,880
Elders.

13
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,810
Did you see that?

14
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,240
I told you.

15
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:52,160
I was telling the truth.

16
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,440
She is indeed a woman.

17
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:53,880
You...

18
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,240
Could it be that

19
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,759
I really traveled to ancient times?

20
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,640
This beard is real too.

21
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,280
Hey!

22
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,160
You girl!

23
00:01:59,160 --> 00:01:59,880
You...

24
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,240
Oh,

25
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,920
this is outrageous!

26
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,400
Everyone, please look.

27
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,640
In my dad's will...

28
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,419
It's written in my father's will.

29
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:11,840
The next head of the family is me, Hu Linglong.

30
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,920
May I ask the elders,

31
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:13,960
in our Hu family's ancestral teachings,

32
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,080
is there any rule that says

33
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,960
a woman cannot inherit the family business?

34
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:17,490
Is there?

35
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,840
Is there?

36
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,320
Well...

37
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,400
It seems not.

38
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,660
Our Hu family's ancestral teachings...

39
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:23,680
It seems

40
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,040
it doesn't specify.

41
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,079
What should we do now?

42
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:29,560
You...

43
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,079
Since that's the case,

44
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,560
I want to ask you, Hu Wenyi.

45
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,000
You keep saying that

46
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,760
a woman cannot inherit the family business.

47
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,360
Then let me ask you,

48
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,600
in the Hu family today,

49
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,800
are your words the golden rule,

50
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:41,130
or do the ancestral teachings come first?

51
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:45,240
The reason it's not specified in the ancestral teachings

52
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:48,400
is because the heads of the Hu family have always been men.

53
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,280
For generations,

54
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,600
it has always been this way.

55
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,440
Haha.

56
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,520
Just because it has always been this way,

57
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,840
does that make it right?

58
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,240
You...

59
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,880
Stop being so glib.

60
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,800
The rule about deceiving the clan members

61
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,200
is clearly written in the ancestral teachings.

62
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,880
According to the ancestral teachings,

63
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,880
you should be expelled from the Hu family.

64
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,480
Men!

65
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,120
Here!

66
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,920
Expel her from the Hu family

67
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,760
and throw her into the mountains.

68
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,360
Men!

69
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:08,920
Yes.

70
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:09,680
Stop!

71
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:10,920
As long as I'm here today,

72
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,640
don't even think about doing anything reckless.

73
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,680
Xu Zhinian.

74
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,850
If you interfere again,

75
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,650
I won't be polite to you.

76
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,120
Don't think just because your father is a police officer,

77
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,960
I wouldn't dare do anything to you.

78
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:22,880
Hu Wenyi.

79
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,480
Let me tell you.

80
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,600
A few days ago, I passed

81
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,720
the selection for the Captain of the Beiyang Fleet.

82
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,360
I am now an official,

83
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,740
a fourth-rank military officer.

84
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,340
A fourth-rank military officer!

85
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:38,740
You can finally realize your ambitions.

86
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,560
If you dare to lay a hand on me,

87
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,400
that would be deliberately murdering an imperial official.

88
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,360
This crime,

89
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,329
can you bear the consequences?

90
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,040
Well...

91
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,079
I need to think of a way

92
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,810
to teach these people a lesson.

93
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,880
Ouch.

94
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,200
Long'er,

95
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,000
what's wrong?

96
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:10,920
What's wrong with her?

97
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,480
Long'er,

98
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,280
what's wrong?

99
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,520
Clan Elder.

100
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:18,600
I, Hu Wenzhong, the sinner of the Hu family.

101
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,640
I, Hu Wenzhong, the sinner of the Hu family,

102
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,880
borrow my unfilial daughter's body

103
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,940
to pay my respects to you, Clan Elder.

104
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,760
This...

105
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,480
You...

106
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,560
Are you...

107
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,200
Wenzhong?

108
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,040
It is I.

109
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,400
Hehe,

110
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,520
are you scared?

111
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:51,800
Linglong disguising herself as a man

112
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,400
to deceive the clan

113
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,120
was forced by me alone.

114
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,560
It was not her wish.

115
00:04:57,560 --> 00:05:00,280
I hope you will not punish her.

116
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:02,000
Having committed such a grave sin,

117
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,800
I now have no face to go to the underworld.

118
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,120
From now on,

119
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,200
I would rather be a wandering ghost

120
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,480
and follow you day and night

121
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,360
to repent for my sins.

122
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,220
That's completely unnecessary.

123
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,360
Ah.

124
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,480
Are you...

125
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,640
Are you Linglong,

126
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,920
or Wenzhong?

127
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,280
Clan Elder,

128
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,320
it's me.

129
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,040
My father just borrowed my body

130
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,800
to pass a message to you.

131
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,320
If you still want to hold him accountable,

132
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:38,760
he will come to find you again tonight.

133
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,720
Never mind.

134
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,960
Respect the dead.

135
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,560
I shouldn't speak nonsense.

136
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,720
I never said

137
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:48,120
I would hold Wenzhong accountable.

138
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:52,080
You are absolutely right, Clan Elder.

139
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,880
But since things have come to this,

140
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,520
as the only daughter of the Hu family,

141
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,320
I am willing to make up for my father's mistakes.

142
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,680
Today, I, Hu Linglong,

143
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,280
if allowed to inherit the position of family head,

144
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:03,600
am willing to devote myself to managing the family business.

145
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,760
I will never marry.

146
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,800
This is my vow.

147
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,520
Manage the family business

148
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,120
and never marry.

149
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,280
Good.

150
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,120
Linglong,

151
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,200
what do you mean by this?

152
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,680
What do I mean?

153
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:24,240
It means I will no longer care about romance,

154
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:26,440
nor will I get involved in love affairs.

155
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,560
I will stay in the Hu family for the rest of my life.

156
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,160
What?

157
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,760
Is it hard to understand?

158
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,520
Shut up!

159
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,840
What nonsense are you talking about?

160
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:33,800
Who are you?

161
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,260
What are your intentions?

162
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,480
But I...

163
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,200
You...

164
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,000
Forget it.

165
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:42,600
Elder,

166
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,360
you absolutely cannot

167
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,159
break our ancestors' rules.

168
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,960
And let a woman

169
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:50,060
succeed as the head of the family!

170
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:50,800
Elder,

171
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,440
I believe you know clearly

172
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,560
why my father

173
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,480
would rather take such great pains

174
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,920
to pass the position to me

175
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,120
than give it to Hu Wenyi.

176
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,480
Sigh.

177
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,080
My ability is obvious to all.

178
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,960
I've never heard anyone question it before.

179
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:04,040
Hu Qingyun doesn't deserve to be the head of the family.

180
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,360
It's only because I revealed my female identity today

181
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,240
that you

182
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,570
look at me differently.

183
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,480
Since it's like this,

184
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,810
why can't I give it a try?

185
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,080
Elder,

186
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:15,160
you can't!

187
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,160
What do you mean

188
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,440
he'd rather pass it to you than me?

189
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:21,160
Speaking sarcastically and talking nonsense!

190
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,160
See if I don't tear your mouth off!

191
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,880
Come on!

192
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:25,560
Linglong.

193
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:26,560
Wenyi,

194
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,280
enough is enough.

195
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,000
Elder.

196
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,600
Enough is enough.

197
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,720
I understand.

198
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,640
I finally understand.

199
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,800
I understand Wenzhong's

200
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,400
good intentions.

201
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,080
Stop arguing, all of you.

202
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,400
What Linglong just said

203
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:51,480
makes some sense.

204
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,080
Today,

205
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:56,920
no matter who I appoint as the head of the Hu family,

206
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,850
someone will be dissatisfied.

207
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,200
In that case,

208
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,480
I will give you

209
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,800
a chance.

210
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,640
Our Hu family,

211
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,920
for hundreds of years,

212
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,960
has taken tea as the foundation of our business.

213
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:09,680
Let's use

214
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,000
a tea competition

215
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,480
to decide the winner.

216
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,120
The more skilled one

217
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,960
can succeed as

218
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:18,400
the new head of the Hu family.

219
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,640
Don't agree to it.

220
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,240
What do you think?

221
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,200
I have lost my sense of smell since childhood.

222
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,360
If it's a tea competition,

223
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,880
I have no chance of winning.

224
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,120
Did you hear that?

225
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,650
Since the Elder has spoken,

226
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,900
of course I am willing to compete.

227
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:37,799
I, Hu Wenyi, have studied the way of tea for decades.

228
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,130
Why would I be afraid of her?

229
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:43,720
Then

230
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,760
what about Linglong?

231
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,520
A tea competition?

232
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:48,440
I've done research with my teacher for years.

233
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,400
Why would I be afraid of these old fogeys?

234
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:50,840
What,

235
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:51,640
scared?

236
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:52,800
Makes sense.

237
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,840
After all, someone who has lost their sense of smell,

238
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:58,280
how could they win a tea competition?

239
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,000
Hahaha.

240
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,520
Strange.

241
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,250
I clearly have a sense of smell.

242
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,880
You must be the original owner of this body.

243
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,240
Flinching before a fight

244
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,840
isn't my, Qiao Xin's, style.

245
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,720
So you can hear me.

246
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,520
Then why did you ignore me just now?

247
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:15,920
Why did you take over my body?

248
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,160
Who exactly are you?

249
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:18,960
My mind is a complete mess right now too.

250
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,640
Oh, don't worry.

251
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,880
I will never harm you.

252
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:21,920
We'll talk later.

253
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,000
Hey!

254
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,400
Answer me first!

255
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:25,600
In that case,

256
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,400
I might as well beat them at their own game.

257
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:27,960
Madam.

258
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,090
How does Hu Wenyi even know about this?

259
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:34,120
It must be because of Dr. Xue.

260
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,000
Linglong.

261
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,720
Is what your Uncle Hu

262
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,320
said just now true or false?

263
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,200
Clan Elder.

264
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,640
He is framing me.

265
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,880
Of course I can smell.

266
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:43,210
I am willing to compete.

267
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,640
Still putting on an act.

268
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,480
It doesn't matter.

269
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,600
When the time comes, you'll be exposed

270
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,130
and thoroughly disgraced.

271
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,120
Good.

272
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,080
Since you're willing to compete,

273
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:56,960
then we

274
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,420
will use a tea competition

275
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,920
to determine the winner.

276
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:03,600
Everyone, please follow me to the back hall.

277
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,480
Linglong.

278
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,040
I haven't seen you for months.

279
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:11,040
How come you seem like a completely different person?

280
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:24,200
I didn't expect to have the chance to compete with ancient people.

281
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,760
Fellow clansmen.

282
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:29,120
According to the rules of our Hu family,

283
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,360
a tea competition

284
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,080
consists of three rounds.

285
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,560
The one who wins two rounds

286
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,360
will be the victor.

287
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,960
Tea has meridians,

288
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,560
and flavor hides profound secrets.

289
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,040
Those with a similar appearance

290
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,440
have different colors and tastes.

291
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,360
This

292
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:47,360
first round

293
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,880
is to identify the tea.

294
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:51,120
The bamboo sieves in front of you

295
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:54,680
contain a mixture from all over,

296
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:57,600
five kinds of tea leaves from different regions.

297
00:10:57,800 --> 00:11:01,280
You need to identify and select them one by one.

298
00:11:01,520 --> 00:11:04,440
Whoever is the fastest and most accurate

299
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,960
will win.

300
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,120
Selecting tea requires observing,

301
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,360
touching,

302
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,320
smelling,

303
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,160
and tasting.

304
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,560
I can't help you.

305
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,460
You can only rely on yourself.

306
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,120
Selecting tea like this

307
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,840
is a bit dull.

308
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,440
Why don't

309
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:29,240
I show you a new trick?

310
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,440
You!

311
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,220
Jiangxi Ninghong.

312
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:50,320
Fujian Tanyang Congou.

313
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,480
Tongmuguan

314
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:06,240
Lapsang Souchong.

315
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:12,680
Clan Elders,

316
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:15,120
please declare me the winner of this round.

317
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,160
Wait, he's wrong.

318
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,680
Authentic Tongmuguan Lapsang Souchong

319
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,040
should melt like tears when exposed to fire.

320
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:26,200
How could it crackle and pop?

321
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,240
This must be an imitation mixed

322
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,760
with roasted tea dust.

323
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,360
Look.

324
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,480
Hu Linglong got it right.

325
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,800
Her nose is quite sharp.

326
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,640
Hu Wenyi is clearly framing her.

327
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:35,360
Yeah.

328
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,480
Everyone is watching, it can't be faked.

329
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,680
When ancient people evaluated tea,

330
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:41,160
they mostly relied on observing the surface and stems,

331
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:43,320
making it hard to notice the subtle details on the leaves.

332
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,120
The back of authentic Tongmuguan Lapsang Souchong leaves

333
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:47,360
should be covered with a crystalline wax.

334
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,440
This is easily overlooked.

335
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,760
I declare that

336
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,560
in the first round,

337
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,220
I, Hu Linglong, am the winner.

338
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:53,680
Hehe.

339
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,800
You're too green

340
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,480
to fight me.

341
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,920
Hmph.

342
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:08,120
It seems she wasn't lying.

343
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,480
She really knows tea.

344
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:13,440
Also, how did my

345
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,880
sense of smell recover?

346
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,840
Strange.

347
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,760
Go.

348
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,760
Yeah.
